snippet.title: Ambition: A Minuet in Power - Story Trailer
snippet.description:
Seduce lovers, snub enemies, and survive the French revolution in a new, roguelike game for PC and Mac.

Learn more at https://ambition-game.com/
Original Score by John Robert Matz, listen to more of his work at http://johnrobertmatz.com/

Support the Kickstarter at https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/joymanufacturingco/ambition-a-minuet-in-power
